divs: Sighting DetailsMy husband saw something in the sky in the backyard. He saw lights above the neighbors shed. Went outside and witnessed to orange red lights in the sky. It passed over our house, looked like a wing and when it passed it covered the stars in the background behind it. Not sure what we saw, but by the time we got to the front of the house it was in the distance and disappeared. During the whole time we seen the flying object there was NO sound.

Summary: 2 red orange lights in sky no sound
